                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d468">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 838.00/1313.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Davis</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Extract.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Port au Prince</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-09-17T09:00:00-04:49">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 17, 1915—9 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Formally recognized Government and signed treaty at 8 o’clock last night. Treaty
                    will be presented to Chambers to-day for ratification. Ratification expected to
                    be had early next week.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Davis</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
